description:
The infinite gems are scattered around the world and only you can collect them!

Crossy Revengers is a crossy road  game that parody the heroes and villains of the popular Avengers movies.
In this game, you'll control some heroes with the sole purpose of collecting the misterious gems that appeared on the streets. But don't think it'll be an easy task: the streets are very dangerous, full of vehicles and obstacles read to stop you on fullfiling your mission!
Are you corageous enough to accept this mission?

<strong>Contents:</strong>
- stages generated dinamically (every stage isn't like another);
- 40 unlockable characters (can you enable all?);
- lots of dangers and collectibles (and some are bad!);
- challenge increases as you reach the end of every stage.

<strong>Controls:</strong>
- press the arrows to move the character through the stage, or to select new characters on the menu screen;
- press the Enter key to start the game, buy new characters on the menu or choose the opitions when losing or reaching the end of each stage;
- press the Esc key to quit the game (when on menu screen).
